On Monday December 16, 2019 I went to this store approximately 11.15 am.  I stood there waiting on a young lady who was on the phone, not speaking to anyone but probably listening to the person on the other side of the call for about 5-7 minutes without even acknowledging me.  I beckoned to a young lady who was coming from the back.  I ordered 3 large 3-topping pizza that I knew were on special because I purchased it normally on Fridays. She tried her best, but could not help because she was quoting me the original price, so she asked the other young lady to help.  Now time is running out because I have a pizza party at my daughter's school and they needed the pizza for 12.15 pm.  The young lady told me that I had to order the pizzas online because they cannot do it in the store.  I told her I'd left my phone at home and I ordered the said pizza at the store all the time when I am unsuccessful online.  She insisted that she couldn't do it because it is an online deal.  I said to her that I understand and now that I know I will try to order them online in the future but for now, I really do not have anymore time to go home to get on the computer and order it. She just turned her back on me, so I ask for management.  I was told by the other young lady that she (the lady who turned her back) was the manager. I went home picked up my phone and returned to the store at about 11.50 and explained to her the problems I was having.  She just said oh I never ordered it online. It did not take her 10 seconds to put in the order. I am thinking what a ridiculous, difficult, inflexible human being. No conscience at all.  First if this is company policy not to take the order in store it should have been said from day one. Secondly, you could have place the order and warn me that this is not company policy seeing that you were the ones who violated the rules in the first place. If this is customer service for this outlet, I do not want to come back and buy anything more pizza from this store.  I realized also that many people are complaining about this outlet.  Do something or else you will be closing down soon.
